import { Container, TextField, Typography} from '@material-ui/core'

const Test3 = () =>{
    return(
        <Container>
            <Typography variant="h3">Text Fields</Typography>
            <form autoComplete="off">
                <TextField
                    color="primary"
                    variant="outlined"
                />

                <TextField
                    color="primary"
                    variant="outlined"
                    fullWidth
                    multiline
                    rows="5"
                    label="Username"
                />
            </form>
        </Container>
    )
}

export default Test3
